translations.en_US:
Applications are ranked according to need. Completion of the Application Does Not Guarantee Service. Please fill out this application and submit online, or print and return by email or USPS to address below:
LandscapeManagement@CharlotteNC.gov
701 Tuckaseegee Rd., Charlotte, NC 28208. Incomplete applications will not be considered. If you need help completing the application, please call 980-259-2771.
